Package main

Class MedicalItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.MedicalItem
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bandage, MedPack, SpacePlagueCure
    public class MedicalItem
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the generic superclass of a medical item, which is used to heal or cure crew members by consuming them
    Author:
    Jackie Qiu

        public boolean equals​(java.lang.Object o)
